uni.bielefeld.cmg.sparkhit.pipeline

Class OnePipe

  • java.lang.Object
    • uni.bielefeld.cmg.sparkhit.pipeline.OnePipe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, Pipeline

    public class OnePipe
extends java.lang.Object
implements Pipeline, java.lang.Runnable
    Returns an object for managing one thread of the pipeline. This class is used in local mode only. For cluster mode, Spark RDD is used to parallelize the tasks.
